Prompt S/R: 提示文本搜索/替换（Prompt S/R）

Process images in a directory on the sam: 处理服务器中某目录的图片，
Use an empty output directory to save pi: 输出到一个单独的空目录中。
Just resize: 直接缩放（不保持长宽比）

Resize and fill: 缩放并填充（保持长宽比）
img2img alternative test: 图转图替代测试（img2img alternative test）
Poor man's outpainting: 穷人的图像扩展（Poor man's outpainting）

Decode CFG scale: 解码提示文本相关性（Decode CFG scale）
Sigma adjustment for finding noise for i: 用于发现图片噪声的 Sigma 调整（adjustment）
Recommended settings: Sampling Steps: 80: 推荐设置： 采样步数：80-100； 采样算法：Euler a； 去噪强度：0.8
Fall-off exponent (lower=higher detail): 衰减指数（Fall-off exponent）（越低细节越好）

CodeFormer weight (0 = maximum effect, 1: CodeFormer 权重（0 = 影响最大；1 = 影响最小）
A merger of the two checkpoints will be: 两个模型的合并结果会生成在你的
Multiplier (M) - set to 0 to get model A: 后续模型比例（设为 0 时只包含模型 A）
Name: 名称
Number of vectors per token: 每个 token 的向量个数
Select activation function of hypernetwo: 为超网络选择激活函数（activation function）
Existing Caption txt Action: 对既存 txt 标题的行为
Train an embedding or Hypernetwork; you: 训练一个模型嵌入或超网络，必须指定一个包含一组 1:1 比例图片的目录
Save an image to log directory every N s: 每 N 步保存一张图片到日志目录，0 为禁用
Save a copy of embedding to log director: 每 N 步保存模型嵌入的副本到日志目录，0 为禁用
Save images with embedding in PNG chunks: 保存图片时将模型嵌入存入 PNG 数据块
Read parameters (prompt, etc...) from tx: 预览时从文转图（txt2img）选项卡读取参数（提示文本等）
Always save all generated images: 始终保存所有生成的图片
Add extended info (seed, prompt) to file: 在宫格图的文件名中加入额外信息（随机种子、提示文本）
Do not save grids consisting of one pict: 不保存单张图片的宫格图
Prevent empty spots in grid (when set to: （在自动检测时）防止宫格图中出现空位
Grid row count; use -1 for autodetect an: 宫格图行数，-1 为自动检测，0 为与批量（Batch size）值相同

Create a text file next to every image w: 保存图片时在其旁边创建记录生成参数的文本文件
Save a copy of image before doing face r: 面部修复前保存图片副本
If PNG image is larger than 4MB or any d: 当 PNG 图片大于 4MB 或某一维大于 4000 像素时，缩小并保存副本为 JPG

When using 'Save' button, only save a si: 使用“保存”按钮时，只保存单张选中的图片
Output directory for images; if empty, d: 图片输出目录，若为空，则默认为下面三个目录
Output directory for grids; if empty, de: 宫格图输出目录，若为空，则默认为下面两个目录
Output directory for txt2img grids: 文转图（txt2img）宫格图输出目录
Output directory for img2img grids: 图转图（img2img）宫格图输出目录
Directory for saving images using the Sa: 用保存按钮将图片保存到的目录
When using \"Save\" button, save images: 使用“保存”按钮时，保存图片到子目录
Max prompt words for [prompt_words] patt: [prompt_words] 模板中提示文本词的最大个数
Tile size for ESRGAN upscalers. 0 = no t: Tile size for ESRGAN upscalers. 0 = no tiling.
Tile overlap, in pixels for ESRGAN upsca: Tile overlap, in pixels for ESRGAN upscalers. Low values = visible seam.
Tile overlap, in pixels for SwinIR. Low: Tile overlap, in pixels for SwinIR. Low values = visible seam.
Upscale latent space image when doing hi: Upscale latent space image when doing hires. fix
CodeFormer weight parameter; 0 = maximum: CodeFormer weight parameter; 0 = maximum effect; 1 = minimum effect
Move face restoration model from VRAM in: Move face restoration model from VRAM into RAM after processing
VRAM usage polls per second during gener: VRAM usage polls per second during generation. Set to 0 to disable.
Always print all generation info to stan: Always print all generation info to standard output
Add a second progress bar to the console: Add a second progress bar to the console that shows progress for an entire job.
Move VAE and CLIP to RAM when training h: Move VAE and CLIP to RAM when training hypernetwork. Saves VRAM.
Number of repeats for a single input ima: Number of repeats for a single input image per epoch; used only for displaying epoch number
Save an csv containing the loss to log d: Save an csv containing the loss to log directory every N steps, 0 to disable
Apply color correction to img2img result: Apply color correction to img2img results to match original colors.
Save a copy of image before applying col: Save a copy of image before applying color correction to img2img results
With img2img, do exactly the amount of s: With img2img, do exactly the amount of steps the slider specifies (normally you'd do less with less denoising).
Enable quantization in K samplers for sh: Enable quantization in K samplers for sharper and cleaner results. This may change existing seeds. Requires restart to apply.
Emphasis: use (text) to make model pay m: Emphasis: use (text) to make model pay more attention to text and [text] to make it pay less attention
Use old emphasis implementation. Can be: Use old emphasis implementation. Can be useful to reproduce old seeds.
Make K-diffusion samplers produce same i: Make K-diffusion samplers produce same images in a batch as when making a single image
Increase coherency by padding from the l: Increase coherency by padding from the last comma within n tokens when using more than 75 tokens
Stop At last layers of CLIP model: Stop At last layers of CLIP model
Interrogate: include ranks of model tags: Interrogate: include ranks of model tags matches in results (Has no effect on caption-based interrogators).
Interrogate: minimum description length: Interrogate: minimum description length (excluding artists, etc..)
CLIP: maximum number of lines in text fi: CLIP: maximum number of lines in text file (0 = No limit)
use spaces for tags in deepbooru: use spaces for tags in deepbooru
escape (\\) brackets in deepbooru (so th: escape (\) brackets in deepbooru (so they are used as literal brackets and not for emphasis)
Show image creation progress every N sam: Show image creation progress every N sampling steps. Set 0 to disable.
Show previews of all images generated in: Show previews of all images generated in a batch as a grid
Show grid in results for web: Show grid in results for web
Do not show any images in results for we: Do not show any images in results for web
Add model hash to generation information: Add model hash to generation information
Add model name to generation information: Add model name to generation information
When reading generation parameters from: When reading generation parameters from text into UI (from PNG info or pasted text), do not change the selected model/checkpoint.
Font for image grids that have text: Font for image grids that have text
Show images zoomed in by default in full: Show images zoomed in by default in full page image viewer
Show generation progress in window title: Show generation progress in window title.
Localization (requires restart): 本地化（应用后重启来变更）
Hide samplers in user interface (require: Hide samplers in user interface (requires restart)
Minimum number of pages per load: 每次加载的最低加载页数
Reload custom script bodies (No ui updat: 重载自定义脚本（无 ui 更新、不重启）
Restart Gradio and Refresh components (C: 重启 Gradio 并刷新组件（仅自定义脚本、ui.py、js 和 css）
Prompt (press Ctrl+Enter or Alt+Enter to: 提示文本（按 Ctrl+Enter 或 Alt+Enter 生成图片）
Negative prompt (press Ctrl+Enter or Alt: 排除文本 （按 Ctrl+Enter 或 Alt+Enter 生成图片）
向提示文本中添加随机画师
Read generation parameters from prompt o: 从提示文本读取生成参数，若无提示文本，则从最后一次生成中读取，并填补至界面
Apply selected styles to current prompt: 在提示文本中应用选中样式
Stop processing images and return any re: 停止处理，返回既存结果
Style to apply; styles have components f: 可用样式；包含提示文本和排除文本
Euler Ancestral - very creative, each ca: Euler Ancestral - 富有创意，每次都能得到完全不同的图，设采样步数到高于 30-40 帮助不大
Denoising Diffusion Implicit Models - be: Denoising Diffusion Implicit Models - 擅长图像修补（Inpaint）
产生一张可以被密铺的图片
Use a two step process to partially crea: 分两步处理，先在较小分辨率下部分地创建一张图片，放大，再在不改变构图的情况下改进细节
Determines how little respect the algori: 决定算法对提供图片的尊重程度。为 0 时，不会改变图片内容；为 1 时，会得到一张无关的图。小于 1.0 的值会导致实际处理所用步数小于指定的采样步数
Classifier Free Guidance Scale - how str: Classifier Free Guidance Scale - 图应与提示文本一致的程度——数值越低越能产生有创意的结果
A value that determines the output of ra: 一个值，用于决定随机数生成器的输出——参数和随机种子完全相同时产生的图片也相同
Set seed to -1, which will cause a new r: 设随机种子为 -1，代表每次都用一个新的随机数
Reuse seed from last generation, mostly: 复用上一次生成时的随机种子，在那个种子是随机得到的情况下最有用
Seed of a different picture to be mixed: 另一张图片的随机种子，会被混入生成中
How strong of a variation to produce. At: How strong of a variation to produce. At 0, there will be no effect. At 1, you will get the complete picture with variation seed (except for ancestral samplers, where you will just get something).
Make an attempt to produce a picture sim: Make an attempt to produce a picture similar to what would have been produced with same seed at specified resolution
用逗号分隔 X 轴的值
用逗号分隔 Y 轴的值
Write image to a directory (default - lo: 保存图片（默认在 log/images），并将生成参数存入 csv 文件
How much to blur the mask before process: 处理前对遮罩模糊的像素数
What to put inside the masked area befor: 处理前要在遮罩区域填入什么内容
fill it with latent space noise: 填入隐空间噪声（latent space noise）
fill it with latent space zeroes: 填入隐空间零点（latent space zeroes）
Upscale masked region to target resoluti: Upscale masked region to target resolution, do inpainting, downscale back and paste into original image
Resize image to target resolution. Unles: Resize image to target resolution. Unless height and width match, you will get incorrect aspect ratio.
Resize the image so that entirety of tar: Resize the image so that entirety of target resolution is filled with the image. Crop parts that stick out.
Resize the image so that entirety of ima: Resize the image so that entirety of image is inside target resolution. Fill empty space with image's colors.
How many times to repeat processing an i: 将图片作为下次迭代的输入重复处理的次数
In loopback mode, on each loop the denoi: 产物迭代模式中，每次迭代去噪强度（Denoising strength）会乘以该值，小于 1 意味着变化程度递减，故生成的图片序列收敛到一张固定图片；大于 1 意味着变化程度递增，故生成的图片序列变得越来越混乱
For SD upscale, how much overlap in pixe: 对于 SD 放大，表示图块间应重叠的像素数，图块重叠使得在合并回一张图片后没有明显可见的接缝
Leave blank to save images to the defaul: 留空以将图像保存到默认路径
Result = A * (1 - M) + B * M: 结果 R = A * (1 - M) + B * M
Result = A + (B - C) * M: 结果 R = A + (B - C) * M

If this option is enabled, watermark wil: If this option is enabled, watermark will not be added to created images. Warning: if you do not add watermark, you may be behaving in an unethical manner.
Use following tags to define how subdire: Use following tags to define how subdirectories for images and grids are chosen: [steps], [cfg], [prompt], [prompt_no_styles], [prompt_spaces], [width], [height], [styles], [sampler], [seed], [model_hash], [prompt_words], [date], [datetime], [job_timestamp]; leave empty for default.
Restore low quality faces using GFPGAN n: 用 GFPGAN 神经网络修复低质量面部
This regular expression will be used ext: This regular expression will be used extract words from filename, and they will be joined using the option below into label text used for training. Leave empty to keep filename text as it is.
This string will be used to join split w: This string will be used to join split words into a single line if the option above is enabled.
List of setting names, separated by comm: List of setting names, separated by commas, for settings that should go to the quick access bar at the top, rather than the usual setting tab. See modules/shared.py for setting names. Requires restarting to apply.
If this values is non-zero, it will be a: If this values is non-zero, it will be added to seed and used to initialize RNG for noises when using samplers with Eta. You can use this to produce even more variation of images, or you can use this to match images of other software if you know what you are doing.
